name: Cyber Cell
description:
Cyber Cell

Make your way though an AI entity. Defeat enemies and turn them to your side to become stonger.

W, A, S, D to move.

Left mouse to attack.

Made for the Brakeys Game Jam 2021.1(Theme: Stronger Together).
